gov.usgs.anss.utility

Class MakeRawToMiniseed

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.utility.MakeRawToMiniseed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MiniSeedOutputHandler

    public class MakeRawToMiniseed
extends java.lang.Object
implements MiniSeedOutputHandler
    This class simplifies creating MiniSeed from a time series. When you create an object of this type the time series is created and Built into an ArrayList of MiniSeed which can be gotten by the user, or written to a file by the appropriate methods. Create one of these for each channel you want to create.
